# Sample configuration file
#
# Please note:
#   o Parameters are CASE SENSITIVE
#   o Parameters must be given in the form 
#        parameter value
#     with one ore more spaces in between
#   o The order of the parameters does not matter
#   o A hash sign is interpreted as a comment

L 4             # Lattice extend, we set T = L in the simulation
s 0             # s parameter for staggered
alpha 0.05      # gauge fixing parameter
taug 0.03       # Langevin integration step size
tuaf 0.02       # Wilson flow integration step size
NRUN 400        # number of configs to generate
NFLOW 20        # number of flow steps
MEAS_FREQ 10    # frequency of measurements outside flow
FLOW_MEAS_FREQ 10    # after how many flow steps do we want to measure?
FLOW_FREQ 10    # after how many Langevin steps do we want to flow?
seed 1234       # random number seed

# reading / writing gauge configurations
read none       # file name for input, 'none' for cold start
write none      # file name for output, 'none' to omit output
